	(175,1,'2015-10-07 03:42:33','2015-10-07 03:42:33','<p class=\"normal\">Our vision is to change the way people go about choosing their careers. We want Forsee to become a verb, not sure what job to do? just Forsee it.</p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\">Our aim is to be a small part of helping to create a society where people truly enjoy their careers. Where people are good at their work and consequently, a lot more productive. Where people are excited to wake up on Monday morning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\">We spend so much time at work so it is massively important to our lives and relationships that our careers are a match for what we like doing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\">I hope you get great insights from Career Navigator and feel free to share your stories and experiences with our team.</p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\">Sincerely,</p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"normal\">Andrew Hartland (use a Digital Signature - not my real one)\r\nManaging Director</p>','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','152-revision-v1','','','2015-10-07 03:42:33','2015-10-07 03:42:33','',152,'http://forsee.com.au/152-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
