	(3373,0,'2016-01-13 11:26:57','2016-01-13 00:26:57','<p>Teach courses in health specialties, in fields such as dentistry, laboratory technology, medicine, pharmacy, public health, therapy and veterinary medicine. Prepare course materials, such as syllabi, homework assignments and handouts. Evaluate and grade students\' class work, assignments and papers. Supervise undergraduate or graduate teaching, internship and research work.</p>\n','University Medical Lecturer','','publish','closed','closed','','university-medical-lecturer','','','2016-01-13 11:26:57','2016-01-13 00:26:57','',0,'http://forsee.192.168.1.200.xip.io:8888/career_desc/university-medical-lecturer/',43,'career_desc','',0),
